description:
Japanese title: Arienēttebayo! Serebu ninpō - Kinton no Jutsu (ありえねーってばよ! セレブ忍法·金遁の術)

Kunijiro visists Tsunade and decides to have Naruto guide his boy through one day in the life of a ninja!
name: Impossible! Celebrity Ninja Art: Money Style Jutsu!

description:
Japanese title: Koko hore wan wan! Maizōkin o sagase (ここ掘れワンワン! 埋蔵金を探せ)

Naruto, Kiba, and Hinata are searching for buried treasue at the request of Tsunade's friend Agari Kaisen. Thinking it's an easy task since they have a map, Tsunade threatens to send them back to the Academy if they fail.
name: The Treasure Hunt is On!

description:
Japanese title: Shissō, Meisō, Jiguzagu sō! Otte owarete machigaete (疾走, 迷走, ジグザグ走!追って追われて間違えて)

After escaping from the cave, Naruto and the others chase after the Kedouin in order to put a halt to their plot, but the Village Hidden in the Leaves is already under attack.
name: Run, Dodge, Zigzag! Chase or Be Chased!

description:
Japanese title: OH!? Purīzu ♥ Misutā Posutoman (OH!?ぷりーず♥みすたーぽすとまん)

Naruto discovers Jiraiya is up to no good. Jiraiya claims to be busy getting his manuscript ready before his deadline. Impatient and irritated, Naruto writes his own manuscript for Jiraiya!
name: Please, Mr. Postman!

description:
Japanese title: Deai "Hoshi" no na o motsu shōnen (出会い 「星」の名を持つ少年)

Hidden Leaf Village receives a request from the Village Hidden in the Stars to guard a star. The star is actually a meteorite that fell 200 years ago and is said to possess mysterious powers.
name: Encounter! The Boy with a Star's Name

description:
Japanese title: Natsuhi Boshi, Omoide no Komori Uta (ナツヒボシ 思い出の子守唄)

Naruto and the others investigates the whereabouts of the stolen star. The team suspects that is an inside job because the ninja who took the star used the ninja art, Kujaku, from the Star Village.
name: The Remembered Lullaby

description:
Japanese title: Hijutsu Kujaku Myōhō no Daishō (秘術 孔雀妙法の代償)

Akahoshi, the masked ninja who kidnapped Sumaru, intends to use Sumaru to call out the mysterious ninja who stole the star.
name: Hidden Jutsu! The Price of the Ninja Art: Kujaku

description:
Japanese title: Hoshikage Hōmurisarareta Shinjutsu (星影 葬り去られた真実)

The masked ninja and Naruto fall into the depths of the Valley. While tending to Naruto's wounds, the masked ninja tells him the reason for stealing the star.
name: Hoshikage: The Buried Truth

description:
Japanese title: Saikai Nokosareta jikan (再会 残された時間)

Natsuhi's body is reacting to the effects of the star. She wields the star and desperately confronts Akahoshi, but Sumaru is taken hostage
name: Reunion: The Remaining Time

description:
Japanese title: Hoshi wa kagayaki o mashite (星は輝きを増して)

Sumaru senses his mother's death and Naruto is unable to stop an angry Sumaru from running off. To save Sumaru, Hokuto and Mizura stake their lives to reveal the truth behind the star training.
name: The Star's Radiance

description:
Japanese title: Inuzuka Kiba no naga~i ichinichi (犬塚キバのなが〜い一日)

Akamaru is injured by a rival shinobi from another nation. The shinobi used a battle skill that spreads bacteria throughout the opponent's body, infecting the vicitim's mental faculties. This causes Akamaru to go into uncontrollable rampage!
name: Kiba's Long Day

description:
Japanese title: Konohagakure no Densetsu, Onbaa wa jitsuzai shita!! (木ノ葉隠れの伝説 オンバアは実在した!!)

A mysterious being attaches itself to Naruto, while he was training in the forest. Tsunade begins to wonder if it isn't the legendary being known as the "Onbaa."
name: A Legend from the Hidden Leaf: The Onbaa!!

description:
Japanese title: Warau Shino (笑うシノ)

Naruto and Shino are given a mission to provide security during the Kagetsu family funeral, but they soon realize that the real mission is to help the eldest son carry out the man's unusual last will and testament!
name: Laughing Shino

description:
Japanese title: Kaigyō!! Konoha hikkoshi sentā (開業!!木ノ葉引越センター)

A ominous black smoke appears over the Land of Greens, and all of sudden Choji and company are attacked by an unidentified Ninja!
name: Open for Business! The Leaf Moving Service

description:
Japanese title: Fukakai, nerawareta gyōshōnin (不可解 狙われた行商人)

While questioning Yurinoshin and Shun, the Hidden Leaf squad learns the truth about Shun's true identity. She is Princess Haruna, the only daughter of the Feudal Lord of the Land of Greens!
name: The Mystery of the Targeted Merchents

description:
Japanese title: Chikasui Mujinzou no ningu (地下水 無尽蔵の忍具)

Naruto and the others is attacked by Ruiga, the first evil ninja, who can draw water from the earth to use as weapons. Naruto soon discovers a way to reverse the odds of their battle!
name: A Limitless Supply of Ninja Tools

description:
Japanese title: Byakugan wa mita! Jiki tsukai no shikaku (白眼は見た!磁気使いの死角)

Naruto is again attacked by the second evil ninja, Jiga. Jiga threatens Naruto's life when Hinata rushes in to save Naruto, but Hinata resists the threats and begins to fight!
name: The Byakugan Sees the Blind Spot!

description:
Japanese title: Shi no Senkoku "Kumori Tokidoki Hare (死の宣告“くもり時々晴れ”)

Naruto and Haruna is confronted by Renga. Declaring that he has taken down others before them, he advances on Naruto, ordering him to hand over the princess!
name: Forecast: Death! Cloudy with Chance of Sun!

description:
Japanese title: Ino zekkyō! Pocchari ♥ Paradaisu (いの絶叫! ポッチャリ♥パラダイス)

The princess has gained weight due to nerves and wants Ino to pose as the princess in order to attend the first meeting with a prince she adores.
name: Ino Screams! Chubby Paradise!

description:
Japanese title: Biba dōjōyaburi! Seishun wa bakuhatsu da (ビバ道場破り! 青春はバクハツだ)

Lee opens a dojo because he feels like he isn't keeping up with his training. He is hoping challengers will come to his dojo to face him in battle.
name: Viva Dojo Challenge! Youth Is All About Passion!

description:
Japanese title: Kaiki, norowareta yureishiro (怪奇 呪われた幽霊城)

The first lady of the Land of Honey and her entourage have disappeared. Naruto, Kiba, and Hinata are sent on a mission and they discover an eerie castle looming in the middle of the road!
name: The Mysterious Curse of the Haunted Castle

description:
Japanese title: Daisan no chōjū, Saidai no raibaru (第三の超獣 最大のライバル)

During Lee's medical check-up, he discovers that there's a lot of damage in his chakra network. Guy tries to cheer him up by taking Lee to the Academy training hall.
name: The Third Super-Beast!

description:
Japanese title: Namida no Gekitotsu! Nekketsu shitei taiketsu (涙の激突! 熱血師弟対決)

Seeking revenge for his dead father, Genho, Yagura's true identity and oldest sibling of the Ryudoin Brothers, confronts Guy using a unique Jutsu.
name: Hot-Blooded Confrontation: Student Vs. Sensei

description:
Japanese title: Daipinchi! Konoha no jūichi nin zen'in shūgō (大ピンチ! 木の葉の11人全員集合)

The ANBU Black Ops suspect that Genno, a carpenter of Hidden Leaf Village, stole important blueprints of the village. Tsunade concludes that the one who used Genno plans to attack the Village and puts the village on Super S-Rank Alert!
name: Crisis: The Hidden Leaf 11 Gather!

description:
Japanese title: ANBU mō teage, Naruto no kioku (暗部もお手上げ ナルトの記憶)

ANBU Black Ops puts Naruto under retro-hypnosis to extract Genno's motives. Without much success, Hidden Waterfall Village will be conducting maneuvers close to the village borders.
name: The Anbu Gives Up: Naruto's Recollection

description:
Japanese title: Matohazure, Mietekita hyōteki (的外れ 見えてきた標的)

While looking for the scattered blueprints, Naruto and his team realize that Genno's actions are a diversion.
name: The Missed Target

description:
Japanese title: Gen'eki baribari, Saikyō no suketto (現役バリバリ 最強の助っ人)

Naruto and the others are shocked at the number of paper bombs placed throughout the village. While removing the seals, unexpected help arrives in the way of Homura and Koharu.
name: The Powerful Helper

description:
Japanese title: Tajū torappu, Hōkai no kauntodaun (多重トラップ 崩壊のカウントダウン)

Naruto confronts Genno, and Shikamaru realizes that all the traps are all diversions. Genno's intention was to bury the village in a rockslide. Can the 11 ninja save the village from destruction?
name: Multiple Traps! Countdown to Destruction

description:
Japanese title: Honjitsu Happyō! "Ninjatachi no ase to namida no Meishōbu Besuto 5! Otanoshimi no bangai hen moaruttebayo Supesharu" (本日発表!「忍者たちの汗と涙の名勝負ベスト5! お楽しみの番外編もあるってばよ」スペシャル)

Naruto, Uzumaki, and Sakura take the microphones as hosts and then the program begins.
name: The Top 5 Ninja Battles!

description:
Japanese title: Kurenai no ketsudan, Torinokosareta Daihappan (紅の決断 とり残された第8班)

Naruto encounters a young girl named Yakumo drawing a strange picture. The ANBU Black Ops and the Medical Corps arrive and whisk her away.
name: Kurenai's Decision: Squad 8 Left Behind

description:
Japanese title: Nerawareta Yakumo, Fūinsareta nōryoku (狙われた八雲 封印された能力)

Naruto has a dream about Yakumo wishing to become a ninja and Kurenai threatens to seal her power
name: Yakumo's Sealed Power

description:
Japanese title: Kurenai no gokuhi ninmu ~Sandaime to no yakusoku~ (紅の極秘任務〜三代目との約束〜)

The assailants are members of the Kurama Clan of Hidden Leaf Village. Naruto and company rush to the villa to protect Yakumo.
name: Kurenai's Top-Secret Mission: The Promise with the Third Hokage

description:
Japanese title: Genjutsu ka genjitsu ka, Gokan o seisuru mono (幻術か現実か 五感を制するもの)

Naruto goes to the hospital, when Unkai the ninja, who attacked them at the villa, appears. They search the village and come up with a theory based on the movement of Shino's parasitic insects.
name: Genjutsu or Reality?

description:
Japanese title:Fūjiraretahazu no nōryoku (封じられたはずの能力)

Naruto finds that Yakumo has put Kurenai in a desperate situation, and the terrible secret of the Kurama villa reveals itself.
name: The Supposed Sealed Ability

description:
Japanese title: Meiki, Kachōfūgetsu no omosa (名器 花鳥風月の重さ)

Naruto and Kiba's mission is to guard a prized tea bowl and meet the client Shinemon.
name: The Weight of the Prized Artifact!

description:
Japanese title: Teki wa "Shinobazu" (敵は「不忍」)

Gantetsu, a member of the Ninja Dropouts requests a guarded escort out of Hidden Leaf Village.
name: The Enemy: Ninja Dropouts

description:
Japanese title:Mayoi no mori (迷いの森)

After evading the ambush by the Ninja Dropouts, Naruto, Gantetsu, and Todoroki find themselves in a forest maze that confuses a human's sense of direction.
name: The Bewildering Forest

description:
Japanese title: Honō no kioku (炎の記憶)

The relationship between Gantetsu and Todoroki is revealed and tensions rise between the two.
name: Memory of Flames

description:
Japanese title: Sorezore no michi (それぞれの道)

After a heated battle, Naruto has the enemy cornered, but a boy is taken. This boy turns out to be Akio, Todoroki's younger brother, who Todoroki thought was dead.
name: To Each His Own Path

description:
Japanese title: Ushinawareta kioku (失われた記憶)

Naruto comes upon an injured youth who has lost his memory. Tsunade is cautious about the boy's presence, but Naruto is impressed by the boys kindness and insists on allowing the boy to stay.
name: Vanished Memories

description:
Japanese title: Torimodoshita genjitsu (取り戻した現実)

Tsunade believes that Menma has some connection to the Hidden Sound Village, and Naruto and the others head to the Land of Rice Paddies to check into Menma's Memories.
name: Bringing Back Reality

description:
Japanese title: Keshi saritai kako (消し去りたい過去)

While in battle, Naruto finds out that Menma is a member of the gang of bandits that attacked their village. Being called a traitor by the leader of the gang, Menma reveals his greatest secret.
name: A Past to Be Erased

description:
Japanese title: Kieta takumi - Nerawareta Shukaku (消えた匠 狙われた守鶴)

Tsunade assigns Shikamaru a mission which is to solve the kidnapping case of the Sand Village ninja candidate Matsuri carried out by the Four Celestials. Leaf genin is called together once again.
name: The Targeted Shukaku

description:
Japanese title: Suna no dōmeikoku - Konoha no shinobi (砂の同盟国 木ノ葉の忍)

Shino, Hinata, and Neji search out the enemy while Shikamaru waits for the right moment to attack. The true intentions of the Four Celestials is to capture Gaara.
name: Sand Alliance with the Leaf Shinobi

description:
Japanese title: Fūjiwareta suna, Suiko no hangeki (封じられた砂 水虎の反撃)

Gaara's opponents are setting up a trap and he is later caught in their secret jutsu, the Reverse Scale Position, and his sand is completely sealed.
name: The Counterattack!

description:
Japanese title: Yomigaetta kyūkyoku heiki (よみがえった究極兵器)

Gaara and Naruto corner Hoko, the last of the Four Celestials, in a gully. They find out that their goal is to steal the Sand Spirit Shukaku's chakra in order to gain the power to challenge the Five Great Nations.
name: The Ultimate Weapon Reborn

description:
Japanese title: Tabidachi (旅立ち)

Gaara transforms into Shukaku the Sand Spirit, and wins an impressive victory. After the battle, some discover new paths to follow, and Naruto decides to become even stronger by going on a training journey with Jiraiya.
name: Departure

deck: Clive refuses Liv's help when one of his former criminal contacts is murdered.
description: When Clive (Malcolm Goodwin) identifies a John Doe in the morgue as one of his former criminal contacts from his days on the vice squad, Liv (Rose McIver) is surprised that Clive is so quick to refuse her help in solving the murder. Liv and Ravi (Rahul Kohli) investigate on their own which puts them in a precarious situation. Liv's problems continue to mount when Major (Robert Buckley) begins searching for a roommate and she believes he's considering a cute co-ed. David Anders also stars.
name: Liv and Let Clive

description: Gordon and Bullock investigate a cold case involving the Ogre, a serial killer who targets young women in Gotham City. Meanwhile, Fish plots her escape from the Dollmaker, and Bruce and Selina confront Reggie.
name: Beasts of Prey

description: Barry (Grant Gustin) is surprised when Felicity Smoak (guest-star Emily Bett Rickards) arrives from Starling City along with her boyfriend, Ray Palmer (guest-star Brandon Routh), who flies in as the Atom. They've come to visit S.T.A.R. Labs as Ray needs help with his suit. Their timing turns out to be fortuitous because it's all hands on deck after a meta human named Brie Larvin (guest star Emily Kinney) unleashes hundreds of robotic bees to attack and kill her former co-workers, including Dr. Tina McGee (guest star Amanda Pays). A group dinner with Barry, Felicity, Ray, Iris (Candice Patton) and Eddie (Rick Cosnett) turns into a disaster.
name: All-Star Team-Up

has_staff_review.name: The Flash Episode #118: "All Star Team Up"

description: Peter becomes a town hero for accidentally finding a missing boy. Meanwhile, Joe decides to live life to the fullest by quitting his job and taking a road trip to Niagara Falls with Peter, Quagmire and Cleveland.
name: JOLO

description: Lance (Paul Blackthorne) continues his mission to take down the Arrow (Stephen Amell) so Felicity (Emily Bett Rickards) orders Oliver to keep a low profile. However, when a meta-human named Jake Simmons (guest star Doug Jones), who kills people with blasts of energy and plasma, starts terrorizing Starling City, Oliver is forced to ask Ray (Brandon Routh) for help. The unlikely duo is forced to team up to save the city.
name: Broken Arrow

description: Robin tries to teach the Titans to respect money, but he ends up as the one who learns the lesson.
name: Two Bumble Bees and A Wasp

description: After attending obedience school, Brian becomes much more submissive, and Peter realizes he misses his old, feistier pal. Meanwhile, Chris makes a new friend at school, but feels betrayed when he discovers it was all a ploy to get closer to Meg.
name: Once Bitten

description: Mordecai and Rigby have to fix the garage door.
name: Garage Door

description: The park guys want to get rid of a very large bird in the park.
name: Brilliant Century Duck Crisis Special

description:
Original English and Japanese title:

English: Terrible Happenings in Heaven!! Garlic Jr. to Become Kami!?

Japanese: Tenkai ga Taihen da!! Gārikku Junia ga Kami ni Naru!? (天界が大変だ!!ガーリックJrが神になる!?)

Gohan’s going fishing, Krillin’s found a girlfriend, and it looks as though peace has once again returned to the Earth. But a terrible evil lurks beneath this tranquil surface: Garlic Junior has escaped from the Dead Zone!
name: The Heavens Tremble

description:
Original English and Japanese:

English: Black Mist of Terror...!! Everyone Turns Demonic.

Japanese: Kyōfu no Kuroi Kiri...!! Minna Mazoku ni Natchatta (恐怖の黒い霧…!!みんな魔族になっちゃった)

With the help of the Spice Boys, Garlic Junior releases the Black Water Mist upon an unsuspecting world. As the dreaded fog spreads, so does Garlic Junior’s control over the Earth!
name: Black Fog of Terror

description:
Original English and Japanese title:

English: The Heavenly Realm is the Battlefield!! Piccolo Becomes Devilish Again...

Japanese: Tenkai ga Senjō da!! Pikkoro ga Mazoku ni Gyaku Modori... (天界が戦場だ!!ピッコロが魔族に逆戻り…)

As Piccolo attempts to hold off the Spice Boys and the infected Z Fighters, Gohan and Krillin race toward Kami’s Lookout to retrieve the one thing capable of reversing the effects of the Black Water Mist: the Sacred Water!
name: Battle in Kami's Lookout
Get That Bigfoot Outa My Face!
It's a Mud, Mud, Mud, Mud World
Journey to the Center of Candace
Dude, We're Getting the Band Back Together
Voyage to the Bottom of Buford

deck: A dangerous new alliance is formed as Coulson and Hunter turn to the last person anyone would expect – Grant Ward! As the war between S.H.I.E.L.D. factions continues, Skye and Lincoln will find themselves drawn into this conflict.
description:
Beginning to distrust Coulson, May orders Simmons to open the toolbox. Simmons doesn't trust her, but reveals that the toolbox is fake and that Fitz has the real one. May tells Gonzales' council that Fitz was responsible.

Coulson, Mike and Hunter lure Ward to a restaurant in Tijuana where they make a deal with him to get to Baron Strucker.
name: The Frenemy Of My Enemy

deck: Attorney Matt Murdock's vigilante crime fighting and his new law practice find equally dangerous challenges in a murder case tied to a corporate crime syndicate.
description: Lawyers Foggy Nelson and Matt Murdoch bribe the police for inside info on fresh cases to drum up potential clients. The first one they find is a woman named Karen Page who was found at the scene of a murder covered in blood and holding the murder weapon. It seems like an open-and-shut case, but Matt believes the woman is innocent.
name: Into the Ring

deck: Murdock makes a near fatal error while trying to save a kidnapped boy, and finds an unlikely ally when he needs saving himself.
description:
In a flashback to when Matt was a child, we learn that Battlin' Jack, Matt's father, was killed by the mob for not taking a dive in a match he was paid off to lose.

In the present, nurse Claire Temple finds Matt's body in a dumpster after his recent attempt to rescue the kidnapped boy. She takes him to her apartment and treats his wounds. But time is running out for the missing boy.
name: Cut Man

description:
Murdock and Foggy take on a mysterious wealthy client, but Murdock is convinced that there's more to the case than just the facts.

Nelson and Murdock are hired by the through a front of the new crime boss in Hell's Kitchen, to take a client who beat a man to death in a bowling alley. Meanwhile Karen is offered a deal to do with the union allies case and Ben Urich investigates the rising crime in New York.
name: Rabbit in a Snowstorm

description: Two vicious Russian brothers working for Fisk strike back against Daredevil. Fisk moves to further consolidate his power in the criminal underworld.
name: In the Blood

description: Fisk moves forward with plans that threaten to rip Hell's Kitchen apart. Murdock and Foggy take on a case helping tenants victimized by a slumlord.
name: World on Fire

description: Daredevil finds himself trapped in the fallout of Fisk's plan to take control of Hell's Kitchen. Ben Urich digs closer to the truth.
name: Condemned

description: An important figure from Murdock's past reemerges seeking his help to battle a new enemy threatening Hell's Kitchen.
name: Stick

description: While Murdock, Foggy and Karen's mission become clearer, Fisk's world spins further out of control in his battle for Hell's Kitchen.
name: Shadows in the Glass

description: When Fisk gains the upper hand, the goal to destroy him becomes even more difficult, while Daredevil faces his own demons.
name: Speak of the Devil

description: Murdock and Foggy's relationship is put to the ultimate test while a new enemy against Fisk emerges.
name: Nelson v. Murdock

description: Fisk and Murdock wrestle with the consequences of their chosen paths, while Ben and Karen get closer to Fisk's true past.
name: The Path of the Righteous

description: Fisk seeks revenge while Karen is haunted by recent events. Daredevil makes a startling discovery about Fisk's financing.
name: The Ones We Leave Behind

description: In the season finale, a boxed-in Fisk and a desperate Murdock, Foggy and Karen are forced to lay their end games.
name: Daredevil

description: Tensions grow in the wake of Wolfe's attempted escape. Wolfe is sought after by Royalle and Walker. A power is murdered.
name: You Are Not It

deck: Greg tells Steven the story of how he met Rose Quartz.
name: Story for Steven

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

name: Does This Duckbill Make Me Look Fat?
